    "elements": [
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "cmt_sub_title",
        "text": "Verses 4-7.",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": " - David mentions himself as the elect of God among all the members of his father's family, and from thence is led to trace the call from the first, by the following steps: - The tribe of Judah (",
        "children": []
